                'biography' => '<p>Margaretha Wulfraet was born in Arnhem in 1678. She learned to paint from her father, Matthijs Wulfraet, and moved to Amsterdam with him in 1681. She is best known for her portraits, landscapes, and genre works. None of her landscape paintings survive. She died in Arnhem in 1760.</p>',
